long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
这个插件可以让使用者通过外网访问本地正在开发的网页。
通过缓存本地正在开发网页的内容实现。

This plugin allows users to access locally developed web pages through an external network.
Implement by caching the content of locally developed web pages.
The validity period of each generated QR code is 10 minutes.
